videoSnippet.title: Major Upset in Pro Chess League - Awonder Liang Beats Hikaru Nakamura
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Watch Naka vs Carlsen Fischer random here http://www.frchess.com/

Here are some of the biggest surprises of the day: Viswanathan Anand drew his first three games. The Minnesota Blizzard smashed the Montreal Chessbrahs. The Pittsburgh Pawngrabbers defeated the Saint Louis Arch Bishops while Awonder Liang beat Fabiano Caruana. Both Super Saturday/Sunday winners, the Armenia Eagles and the San Jose Hackers, failed to win their matches.

Read the entire article here https://www.chess.com/news/view/liang-defeats-caruana-in-thrilling-day-of-pro-chess-upsets-2439

Hikaru Nakamura vs Awonder Liang
Pro Chess League (2018), chess.com INT, rd 4, Feb-03
